08:48.302 --> 08:51.507
So are the books coming in quite systematically then by shelving?

08:51.567 --> 08:53.490
So are they starting low and moving up?

08:53.530 --> 08:55.894
They've actually started, I think it's basically before.

08:56.214 --> 09:05.690
